Rate the quality of simplified sentences in English

This study aims to collect ratings for the simplification of patent sentences, which are considered difficult to read and understand.

The collected data will be used for research only. However, the data will be made available to other researchers, and the results of this investigation may be published in scientific venues and used in further studies.



To participate in this experiment, you must:

	Be an English native speaker
	Be at least 18 years old and competent to provide consent
	Have read and understood the information provided about the research project
	Agree for the data collected to be used in an anonymized way in the future
	Agree to take part in the research previously described



I accept to participate in this research.
